Package: pophelperSpatial
Type: Package
Title: Spatial plots for q-matrices/qlists
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2016-12-22
Author: Roy Mathew Francis
Authors@R: person("Roy", "Francis", email = "roy.m.francis@outlook.com",role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Roy Mathew Francis <roy.m.francis@outlook.com>
Description: A set of useful functions for incorporating spatial data with qlist or q-matrices 
    such as output from STRUCTURE, TESS, ADMIXTURE, fastSTRUCTURE etc. This package 
    works along side the pophelper package.
URL: https://github.com/royfrancis/pophelperSpatial
